TinyMake version 0.02
=====================

This module provides a way of building software similar to make or rake.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

  File::Find

